OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMetric measure rules to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstay after Brexit review   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has confirmed it is not 
OL,6, planning to change the rules on selling
OL,7, in imperial measures after Brexit.     
OL,9,FMinisters looked at changing laws      
OL,10,Finherited from the EU that mean traders
OL,11,Fcan use Britain's traditional weighing 
OL,12,Fsystem only alongside the metric one.  
OL,14,FBut they have now decided not to, after
OL,15,Fnearly 99% of respondents to an        
OL,16,Fofficial consultation said they were   
OL,17,Fhappy with kilos and litres.           
OL,19,FHowever, post-Brexit changes are on the
OL,20,Fway for wine sold in shops.            
